  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">International Day of the Girl Child 2020 - Rainbo Initiative &amp; CoP on Gender</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The &#x2018;support to the Community of Practice on GBV&#x2019; project in Sierra Leone, implemented through Rainbow Initiative for the Celebration of the International Day of the Girl Child aims to promote girl&#x2019;s empowerment and fulfilment of their human rights while also highlighting the challenges that girls are face with. The objective of the grant is to support girls in communities to amplify their voices, raise awareness on the importance of their education, SGBV and other forms of discrimination against girls and stand up for their rights.  The key activities include organizing community awareness through production of information, education and communication materials, school-based activities, media advocacy through radio talk shows to commemorate this day in selected communities.</narrative>
  </description>
